 Da, pa imate šta i zapustiti.

398
00:49:02,660 --> 00:49:05,880
 Pa to nije problem kad neko zna pjevat.

399
00:49:05,880 --> 00:49:07,560
 Mi smo, kad smo bili djeca,

400
00:49:07,560 --> 00:49:09,140
 onda, kad bi s tato i mamu putovali,

401
00:49:09,140 --> 00:49:12,100
 onda bi oni, da bi nas zabavljali,

402
00:49:12,100 --> 00:49:13,840
 kad bi nam putovanja bila dosadna,

403
00:49:13,840 --> 00:49:15,940
 ono, kad bi počeli ispitivati,

404
00:49:15,940 --> 00:49:17,660
 kad ćemo stić, kad ćemo stić,

405
00:49:17,660 --> 00:49:20,020
 to ćete još vidjeti sa svojim matejem,

406
00:49:20,020 --> 00:49:21,340
 kako to izgleda.

407
00:49:21,340 --> 00:49:23,880
 Onda bi mama i tata nam rekli,

408
00:49:23,880 --> 00:49:25,600
 da dobro natjecanje u pjevanju,

409
00:49:25,600 --> 00:49:27,280
 da imamo u autu.

410
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:28,640
 I onda bi mi pjevali,

411
00:49:28,640 --> 00:49:30,820
 oni bi ocjenjivali i zabavili bi se tako.

412
00:49:30,820 --> 00:49:32,980
 Ali onda smo mi jako brzo shvatili,

413
00:49:32,980 --> 00:49:35,800
 da u stvari pjesma koja dobije najviše bodova,

414
00:49:35,800 --> 00:49:37,860
 da su uvijek pjesme od vice Vukova.

415
00:49:38,220 --> 00:49:39,380
 I to posebno je moj dom.

416
00:49:39,380 --> 00:49:42,220
 I onda smo se borili,

417
00:49:42,220 --> 00:49:44,900
 koji će prvi od pjeca uspjevati Vicu Vukova.

418
00:49:44,900 --> 00:49:46,860
 Onda su nam rekli,

419
00:49:46,860 --> 00:49:48,460
 stop, stop, stop, ne može tako.

420
00:49:48,460 --> 00:49:49,680
 Ovo me pocijetilo,

421
00:49:49,680 --> 00:49:51,500
 rekli ste da ste i vi njegov fani,

422
00:49:51,500 --> 00:49:52,560
 ja sam isto doista,

423
00:49:52,560 --> 00:49:54,880
 on je, koliko je ta njegova,

424
00:49:54,880 --> 00:49:58,260
 koliko je on značio za ljude u Hrvatskoj,

425
00:49:58,260 --> 00:50:00,020
 taj njegov glas, njegove pjesme,

426
00:50:00,020 --> 00:50:02,120
 koji je utjecaj to imalo, nevjerojatno.

427
00:50:02,120 --> 00:50:02,560
 Da.

428
00:50:02,560 --> 00:50:06,520
 Nevjerojatno što divna pjesma

429
00:50:06,520 --> 00:50:08,520
 može napraviti za generacije ljudi.

430
00:50:08,520 --> 00:50:09,840
 Posebno na

431
00:50:09,840 --> 00:50:12,960
 Tu ćeš naći uvijek dom.

432
00:50:12,960 --> 00:50:15,460
 Da, posebno tako isto.

433
00:50:15,460 --> 00:50:18,680
 Dobro, Stjepo, ja se nadam da ćemo uskoro

434
00:50:18,680 --> 00:50:21,820
 vas moći i na koncertima gledati,

435
00:50:21,820 --> 00:50:24,080
 da ćete ovaj vaš album imat priliku

436
00:50:24,080 --> 00:50:26,340
 predstaviti u živo publici,

437
00:50:26,340 --> 00:50:28,380
 dakle, vaš album moja Hridino.

438
00:50:28,380 --> 00:50:30,480
 Je li nešto u planu uskoro?

439
00:50:30,480 --> 00:50:36,460
 Je, ovako, u Zagrebu sam 26. ožujka,

440
00:50:36,520 --> 00:50:38,480
 u Župi Remete,

441
00:50:38,480 --> 00:50:41,300
 u Zneseneja Blažene Djevice Marije,

442
00:50:41,300 --> 00:50:42,800
 imat ću jedan svoj nastup,

443
00:50:42,800 --> 00:50:43,760
 gore koncert,

444
00:50:43,760 --> 00:50:45,360
 bit će misa, klanjanje,

445
00:50:45,360 --> 00:50:46,840
 i onda poslije mise će biti

446
00:50:46,840 --> 00:50:48,300
 moj nastup,

447
00:50:48,300 --> 00:50:50,560
 gdje ću izvoditi pjesme

448
00:50:50,560 --> 00:50:51,560
 s albuma Moja Hridino.

449
00:50:52,080 --> 00:50:54,360
 To su moje lijepe meditativne pjesme,

450
00:50:54,360 --> 00:50:55,300
 gdje je u biti,

451
00:50:55,300 --> 00:50:55,880
 ja sam,

452
00:50:55,880 --> 00:50:57,540
 meni kažu ljudi,

453
00:50:57,540 --> 00:50:58,620
 kaže, ti pjevaš onako dosta,

454
00:50:58,620 --> 00:50:59,560
 onako tužne pjesme,

455
00:50:59,560 --> 00:51:00,580
 ali u biti nisu tužne,

456
00:51:00,580 --> 00:51:02,680
 one su radice u psalmima,

457
00:51:02,680 --> 00:51:04,060
 pokajničkim posebno.

458
00:51:04,060 --> 00:51:05,320
 Ja sam pjevač korizme,

459
00:51:05,320 --> 00:51:06,260
 jao, jednostavno,

460
00:51:06,260 --> 00:51:08,700
 možda je to za moju dušu najbolje.

461
00:51:08,700 --> 00:51:11,360
 Onda volim paš Davidove psalme,

462
00:51:11,360 --> 00:51:13,240
 koji su baš onako pokajnički.

463
00:51:13,240 --> 00:51:14,280
 Ono, Bože moj, gdje si?

464
00:51:14,400 --> 00:51:14,960
 Trebam te.

465
00:51:14,960 --> 00:51:16,120
 Hridino moja,

466
00:51:16,120 --> 00:51:16,860
 tonem.

467
00:51:16,860 --> 00:51:18,000
 I onda to,

468
00:51:18,000 --> 00:51:18,900
 kad ja to izvodim,

469
00:51:18,900 --> 00:51:19,580
 onda vjerovatno,

470
00:51:19,580 --> 00:51:20,820
 kako smo mi većina,

471
00:51:20,820 --> 00:51:21,400
 svi ranjeni,

472
00:51:21,400 --> 00:51:24,040
 jer nitko nije bez grijeha,

473
00:51:24,040 --> 00:51:24,840
 svi smo s grijehom,

474
00:51:24,840 --> 00:51:26,520
 onda svi osjetimo u tome,

475
00:51:26,520 --> 00:51:27,400
 utjehu ono,

476
00:51:27,400 --> 00:51:28,460
 pa to sam ja,

477
00:51:28,460 --> 00:51:29,620
 meni je teško,

478
00:51:29,620 --> 00:51:30,880
 ja dva pijem za Bogom.

479
00:51:30,880 --> 00:51:31,980
 Upravo je rekuo ono,

480
00:51:31,980 --> 00:51:32,820
 što ja želim reći,

481
00:51:32,820 --> 00:51:34,120
 ali nisam znao izreći.

482
00:51:34,120 --> 00:51:36,220
 I to se događa u biti psalmu 18,

483
00:51:36,220 --> 00:51:37,280
 to taknime Isuse

484
00:51:37,280 --> 00:51:39,500
 i svim ovim pjesmama sa albumom.

485
00:51:39,640 --> 00:51:41,000
 Treći mjesec u Zagrebu,

486
00:51:41,000 --> 00:51:41,400
 dobro,

487
00:51:41,400 --> 00:51:43,000
 i nadamo se da će biti još koncerata,

488
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:45,100
 sad kad se malo stvari poprave.

489
00:51:45,100 --> 00:51:46,400
 Sada je lijeto biti će,

490
00:51:46,400 --> 00:51:47,840
 najavljaju se nešto i u Solinu,

491
00:51:47,840 --> 00:51:48,600
 možda u Splitu,

492
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:51,940
 ima ću i u Međugorju neke nastupe.

493
00:51:51,940 --> 00:51:53,160
 Ima ću u Kočerinu,

494
00:51:53,160 --> 00:51:54,320
 isto sa kod Fra Marija,

495
00:51:54,320 --> 00:51:55,400
 kad smo već njega spomenuli,

496
00:51:55,400 --> 00:51:58,400
 sedamnesti ožujka ove godine,

497
00:51:58,400 --> 00:52:01,780
 sam isto ću imati nastup i svjedočanstvo

498
00:52:01,780 --> 00:52:04,280
 u Kočerinu ili u BiH.

499
00:52:04,280 --> 00:52:05,640
 Super, super.

500
00:52:05,640 --> 00:52:07,960
 Evo, puno hvala, Stjepo,

501
00:52:08,020 --> 00:52:09,240
 na ovom razgoru,

502
00:52:09,240 --> 00:52:10,860
 na ovim divnim pjesmama

503
00:52:10,860 --> 00:52:12,220
 koje ste s nama podijelili.

504
00:52:12,220 --> 00:52:14,240
 I evo, radojem se

505
00:52:14,240 --> 00:52:16,680
 novim, novim vašim pjesmama

506
00:52:16,680 --> 00:52:19,460
 i trilikama da vas joj živo čujemo.

507
00:52:19,460 --> 00:52:21,000
 Evo, moj život osobnosti

508
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:22,760
 izbiljamo bogatili svojom glazbom

509
00:52:22,760 --> 00:52:24,400
 i vjerujem da je tako za puno ljudi.

510
00:52:25,080 --> 00:52:27,140
 Slava Bogu, slava Isusu našemu dragome

511
00:52:27,140 --> 00:52:28,840
 i album je vaš u pripremi.

512
00:52:28,840 --> 00:52:30,120
 Već imam spisak pjesama,

513
00:52:30,120 --> 00:52:31,940
 već pjesme manje više imam,

514
00:52:31,940 --> 00:52:33,080
 sad joj se već snimaju

515
00:52:33,080 --> 00:52:34,300
 i uskoro će sigurno,

516
00:52:34,300 --> 00:52:35,420
 ja vjerujem da će ove godine

517
00:52:35,420 --> 00:52:36,240
 već album izaći,

518
00:52:36,240 --> 00:52:36,820
 novi album,

519
00:52:36,820 --> 00:52:37,720
 tako da idemo,

520
00:52:38,300 --> 00:52:39,120
 Moja Hridino 2.

521
00:52:39,120 --> 00:52:41,300
 Može, ali da vam samo još pitam,

522
00:52:41,300 --> 00:52:43,160
 gdje ljudi mogu kupiti

523
00:52:43,160 --> 00:52:44,100
 Moja Hridino 1?

524
00:52:44,100 --> 00:52:45,900
 To me je dosta ljudi već pitalo.

525
00:52:45,900 --> 00:52:48,600
 Znači, CD se može nabaviti

526
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,220
 najbolje preko moje službene

527
00:52:50,220 --> 00:52:53,880
 internet stranice www.markos.com

528
00:52:53,880 --> 00:52:54,760
 K.K.O. Karlovac,

529
00:52:54,760 --> 00:52:55,320
 Markos,

530
00:52:55,320 --> 00:52:57,620
 i tu se album može naručiti,

531
00:52:57,620 --> 00:52:58,920
 može se dobiti i autogram

532
00:52:58,920 --> 00:53:00,540
 i brzo dođe,

533
00:53:00,540 --> 00:53:01,480
 dođe kroz dan, dva,

534
00:53:01,480 --> 00:53:02,780
 ovako riječ u Hrvatskoj,

535
00:53:02,780 --> 00:53:04,820
 može se naručiti iz inozemstva,

536
00:53:04,820 --> 00:53:05,940
 tako da, evo,

537
00:53:05,940 --> 00:53:07,660
 album se može naručiti

538
00:53:07,660 --> 00:53:08,860
 najprije i najbolje

539
00:53:08,860 --> 00:53:09,980
 preko moje internet stranice,

540
00:53:09,980 --> 00:53:10,380
 a naravno,

541
00:53:10,380 --> 00:53:12,220
 onda postoje i druga prodajna mjesta

542
00:53:12,220 --> 00:53:14,200
 gdje se ne može dobiti autogram,

543
00:53:14,200 --> 00:53:16,340
 ali to su i Laudato,

544
00:53:16,340 --> 00:53:17,420
 televizija i Verbum.

545
00:53:17,420 --> 00:53:19,740
 Super, super, dobro.

546
00:53:19,740 --> 00:53:20,900
 Evo, vjerujem da će to

547
00:53:20,900 --> 00:53:23,400
 mnogi iskoristiti priliku.

548
00:53:23,400 --> 00:53:25,080
 Hvala lijepa i svako dobro

549
00:53:25,080 --> 00:53:26,640
 pozdravljam vas Dubrovniku

550
00:53:26,640 --> 00:53:27,620
 i cijelu vašu obitelj.

551
00:53:27,620 --> 00:53:30,100
 Hvala vama i lijepi vam pozdrav

552
00:53:30,100 --> 00:53:31,780
 i Boži blagoslov vama,

553
00:53:31,780 --> 00:53:34,440
 vašu obitelj i svima koji će ovo gledati

554
00:53:34,440 --> 00:53:35,340
 i koji će slušati.

555
00:53:35,340 --> 00:53:37,040
 Dragi gledatelji,

556
00:53:37,040 --> 00:53:39,660
 puno vam hvala da pratite 55 minuta

557
00:53:39,660 --> 00:53:41,780
 i pozdravljam vas do sljedećeg.

558
00:53:50,900 --> 00:54:11,140
 Hvala lijepa i svima koji će ovo gledati.

